  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Combine your <strong>egg[s]</strong>, most of your <strong>cornflour</strong> (save a little for later!) and 35g <span class=\"text-purple\">[45g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[60g]</span> <strong>flour </strong>in a jug, then gradually whisk in 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[100ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[130ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> and 25ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[30ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>batter</strong> in the fridge to rest</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-3-1714736050853-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-3-1714736050853-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-3-1714736050853-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-3-1714736050853-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-3-1714736050853-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>sausages</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-12 min or until the sausages are beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1714736061882-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1714736061882-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1714736061882-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1714736061882-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1714736061882-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sausages are browning, top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> into batons and trim your <strong>green</strong> <strong>beans</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>carrot batons </strong>and <strong>green</strong> <strong>beans</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin</strong> <strong>foil</strong> with a splash of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the veg to form a tightly sealed parcel and add to a baking tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Make 2 separate parcels!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-3-1714736066033-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-3-1714736066033-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-3-1714736066033-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-3-1714736066033-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-3-1714736066033-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free sausages have browned, carefully pour the <strong>rested</strong> <strong>batter</strong> into the dish</p><p>Return the dish to the oven along with the veg parcel[s] and cook for 22-25 min, or until the batter is golden, the sausages are cooked through and the veg is tender – this is your <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>toad in the hole &</strong> <strong>steamed veg</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't peek! Opening the oven might make your giant Yorkie collapse!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-3-1714736070268-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-3-1714736070268-x400.jpg",
