    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p><p>Return the potatoes to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
