    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cornflour</strong> and <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> in a jug with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Gradually add 120ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[180ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[240ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and stir in your <strong>onion</strong> <strong>marmalade</strong> – this is your <strong>gravy mix</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>gravy</strong> <strong>mix</strong> in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 2 min or until thickened, stirring halfway – this is your <strong>onion</strong> <strong>gravy</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
